snippet.title: Super Thor Quest (SNES) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Get actual SNES cartridge here: https://www.pikointeractive.com/store.html#!/Super-Thor-Quest-SNES/p/50560385/category=14008401

A classic arcade platformer SNES homebrew game. Help Thor to save Lady Sif from the Snow man!

Thor Quest for SNES features four different levels of increasing difficulty in awesome 16-bit graphics and sound!
